        <div class="instructions">
            <h3>INSTRUCTIONS:</h3>
            <p><strong>Manual Input:</strong> Enter values in Year 1 row only</p>
            <p><strong>Red Column (A):</strong> Increases by selected rate (8–14%)</p>
            <p><strong>Green B:</strong> 0.00% – stays flat</p>
            <p><strong>Green C:</strong> +1.99% per year</p>
            <p><strong>Green D:</strong> +2.99% per year</p>
            <p><strong>All values rounded to nearest cent and shown with $</strong></p>
